    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Key enthusiast maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry, offering precise turn-in and excellent chassis communication. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust with recent valve clearances performed. A true driver\u2019s car optimized for performance and longevity.",
