      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-maintained, reliable performer that remains in solid overall condition. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, though a careful walk-around will reveal minor road-derived stone chips on the hood and a small, faint scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. The alloy wheels are clean with no significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin is remarkably preserved; the leather seating is free of tears or stains, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every feature, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the high-fidelity audio system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet, backed by a comprehensive service history that includes a recent fluid flush and brake pad replacement. The car tracks straight, brakes firmly, and offers a smooth, confident ride. This is a complete, honest car perfect for someone who values mechanical integrity and a clean, presentable aesthetic.",
